{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the Production and Sale of Lab-Grown Meat",
        "additional_details": "We urge the Government to prohibit the commercial production, sale, and importation of lab-grown meat for human consumption in the UK in order to:\r\n- Protect traditional livestock farming and rural economies\r\n- Uphold high food safety, animal welfare, and transparency standards\r\n- Apply the precautionary principle to novel food technologies",
        "background": "We call on the UK Government to introduce legislation banning the production, sale, and importation of lab-grown (cell-cultured) meat for human consumption, following the precautionary approach already adopted by countries such as Italy.",
